@page "/profile/max"
<h2 class="text-center">Meet Max: The Adventurer</h2>

<div class="text-center mt-4">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1592197652418-64c6d2e2d886"
         alt="Max"
         class="img-fluid"
         style="width: 500px; height: 500px; object-fit: cover;">
</div>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <p>
        Max is a spirited Border Collie mix who lives for adventure. Whether it’s hiking trails, chasing frisbees, or learning new tricks, Max is always up for a challenge.
    </p>
    <p>
        He’s intelligent, energetic, and eager to please, making him the ideal companion for an active individual or family.
    </p>
    <div class="text-center mt-3">
        <form action="/submit" method="POST">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="window.location.href='/application-page'; return false;">Submit Application</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

